{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.000", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.520", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.320", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2011 wurde im Deutschen Bundestag eine Expertenkommission eingerichtet\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.360", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar mit externen Experten wie Herrn Professor Dr.\u00a0Bryde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.361", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ehemaliger Verfassungsrichter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.361", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.362", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und vielen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.362", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.363", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vielen weiteren Pers\u00f6nlichkeiten des \u00f6ffentlichen und gesellschaftlichen Lebens\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.363", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.364", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die dar\u00fcber beraten und uns Vorschl\u00e4ge machen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.364", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.365", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie diese leidige Frage der Festsetzung der H\u00f6he der Abgeordnetenbez\u00fcge geregelt werden kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.365", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.366", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In einem Bericht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.366", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.480", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den wir in der letzten Legislaturperiode intensiv diskutiert haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.200", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wurden Empfehlungen dazu abgegeben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.080", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es stellte sich die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nach welchem Mechanismus eigentlich eine j\u00e4hrliche Anpassung bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.800", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcberhaupt eine Anpassung der Abgeordnetenbez\u00fcge stattfinden soll\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob in Ein-, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.200", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zwei- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.760", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder Dreijahresschritten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.640", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und woran sich die H\u00f6he der Abgeordnetenentsch\u00e4digung orientiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.120", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das alles ist offen und transparent dargelegt worden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.640", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war ein positives Moment dieser Expertenkommission, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.760", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der wir sehr dankbar f\u00fcr diese Vorschl\u00e4ge waren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.840", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn dadurch wurde zum ersten Mal transparent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.841", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nach welchen Kriterien und in welcher H\u00f6he Abgeordneten\u00adentsch\u00e4digungen festgelegt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.841", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.842", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So weit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.842", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.843", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so gut."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.843", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.844", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nun gibt es f\u00fcr diesen neuen Bundestag folgende Verpflichtung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.844", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.040", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Anpassungsmechanismus im \u00a7\u00a011 Abgeordnetengesetz muss von diesem neu gew\u00e4hlten Deutschen Bundestag best\u00e4tigt werden.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.280", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.840", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jetzt frage ich mich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo liegt denn eigentlich der Skandal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.640", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den hier manche herbeischreien wollen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.641", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es peinlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.641", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.642", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier war gerade von Scham die Rede. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.642", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.643", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcrde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.643", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.360", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4re ich der Erste Parlamentarische Gesch\u00e4ftsf\u00fchrer der AfD oder Mitarbeiter seiner Verwaltungsleitung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.840", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Erdboden versinken angesichts der Debatte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.240", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir hier f\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.160", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn wir haben am 13.\u00a0Oktober im Vor\u00e4ltestenrat das erste Mal dar\u00fcber geredet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.480", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Anpassungsmechanismus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.560", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den dieses Gesetz vorsieht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.840", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vom Deutschen Bundestag verl\u00e4ngert werden muss und dass das bis zur dritten Kalenderwoche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Januar\u00a02018, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.280", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu erfolgen hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kein Widerspruch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.521", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "keine Wortmeldung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.521", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.080", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kein Wortbeitrag der AfD."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.840", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und dann reden wir hier mit den Damen und Herren \u00fcber Scham oder Peinlichkeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.760", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr muss ich bei dieser Debatte nur nach rechts gucken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.800", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben am 11.\u00a0Dezember 2017 in der Runde der Parlamentarischen Gesch\u00e4ftsf\u00fchrerinnen und Gesch\u00e4ftsf\u00fchrer wieder \u00fcber dieses Thema geredet und vereinbart, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.880", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "heute dazu im Deutschen Bundestag eine Beschlussfassung vorzunehmen und diesen Punkt auf die Tagesordnung zu setzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.480", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gab weder einen Widerspruch vonseiten des Ersten Parlamentarischen Gesch\u00e4ftsf\u00fchrers noch eine inhaltliche Anmerkung zum Thema."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.200", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Ha\u00dfelmann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.160", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da werden hier heute die Backen so aufgeblasen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie scheinheilig ist das denn?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.440", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Ha\u00dfelmann!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.480", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.960", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich lasse keine Frage zu.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.040", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie scheinheilig ist das denn?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin fast am Ende meiner Redezeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.480", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zuletzt h\u00f6re ich von Journalisten: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.520", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mein Gott, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.200", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die AfD h\u00e4tte sich auch noch darum k\u00fcmmern m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.200", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das \u00fcberhaupt zur Sprache kommt.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.640", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was f\u00fcr ein Bl\u00f6dsinn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.160", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.120", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die haben noch nicht einmal einen Antrag auf Aussprache gestellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.160", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der kam von der CDU/CSU. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.560", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So ist die Lage."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.880", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und jetzt sage ich mal: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.320", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer meint, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.200", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier im Parlament uns vorf\u00fchren zu k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.720", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der muss fr\u00fcher aufstehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.760", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.480", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.000", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Wort zu einer Kurzintervention hat der von Frau Ha\u00dfelmann angesprochene Dr.\u00a0Baumann."
   ]
  }
 ]
}